args.code:
from PyPDF2 import PdfReader

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/9-GDPZero/GDPZero/paper.pdf'
reader = PdfReader(pdf_path)

# Extract the first 3 pages for initial context
text = ''
for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages[:3]):
    text += page.extract_text() + '\n---PAGE BREAK---\n'

print(text[:2000])
